# RCA Bot Routine — Environment Variables
#
# No custom environment needed for any of the 3 Routines.
#
# All authentication is handled by the connectors configured in the Routine:
#   - Jira auth    → Atlassian connector (OAuth)
#   - Teams auth   → Microsoft 365 connector (OAuth)
#   - Claude API   → built into the Routine runtime (Enterprise credentials)
#
# The Teams meeting chat thread ID is hardcoded in routines/reminder.md.
# Update it there if the recurring meeting series is ever recreated.
